{"tid":1141251,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"女上司西到仆街 俾你會點揀","createTime":"2019-05-06T10:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T11:25:09.000Z","uid":93379,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"636f2ee4a1912113c092e80889cb690b32158299","tid":1141251,"uid":93379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"成日將d野射撚曬俾我做自己係度hea鳩鳩傾電話玩電話<br />\n<br />\n經常性冇野搵野做博上位但所有ground work又係射曬落黎 原本準時放工都要ot 甚至放假都要冇補水咁做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己做錯扮冇事 我做錯小小就send email cap曬圖屌鳩你<br />\n<br />\n每日心情唔同 同一件事之前都係咁做 今日都可以屌你做錯<br />\n<br />\n每日番工都好想裸辭 唔想再對住個西女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但出去未必搵到而家個人工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正評：裸辭唔撚做狗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負評：死都頂落去 唔好同錢過唔去"},{"pid":"76149f4c33f7196fd8b391dffa03c435a12b30bb","tid":1141251,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:55:59.000Z","msg":"幾錢人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a517961c7c6543f483388bdffa12c7381f1accb2","tid":1141251,"uid":93379,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"76149f4c33f7196fd8b391dffa03c435a12b30bb","tid":1141251,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:55:59.000Z","msg":"幾錢人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:03:45.000Z","msg":"18fg計曬所有野 24k/m<br />\n<br />\n但自知廢J 入到呢間都算好彩"},{"pid":"1d1f53e5060c92eaac0c69277e35b2b84e6cb5a6","tid":1141251,"uid":109655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:04:42.000Z","msg":"幫佢奶閪"},{"pid":"b70d8255aaa99e05e7261a83d50cfe6a53e38376","tid":1141251,"uid":113373,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n星期六 早上9點 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">事態危急</span><br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律  <span style=\"color: red;\">無需證據 無需理由</span><br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></strong>"},{"pid":"161e7e228f5023179400bae5305927220bd98ab7","tid":1141251,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a517961c7c6543f483388bdffa12c7381f1accb2","tid":1141251,"uid":93379,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"76149f4c33f7196fd8b391dffa03c435a12b30bb","tid":1141251,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:55:59.000Z","msg":"幾錢人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:03:45.000Z","msg":"18fg計曬所有野 24k/m<br />\n<br />\n但自知廢J 入到呢間都算好彩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:06:51.000Z","msg":"咁的確算唔錯喎,邊行呀"},{"pid":"991b659e5833154c2a82c7643e15f4aa115770b8","tid":1141251,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:16:13.000Z","msg":"學識溝通問清問楚"},{"pid":"e141ae66c05ee252fe9b2e973fdd5b3f2028120e","tid":1141251,"uid":93379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"161e7e228f5023179400bae5305927220bd98ab7","tid":1141251,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a517961c7c6543f483388bdffa12c7381f1accb2","tid":1141251,"uid":93379,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"76149f4c33f7196fd8b391dffa03c435a12b30bb","tid":1141251,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:55:59.000Z","msg":"幾錢人工<img src=\"/